Exception : an exception in java is an event which occurs during the Exception of the program,that disrupts the normal
flow of the program's instructions to overcome this we use Exception handling in java.

Exception handling : 
it is powerful mechanism to handle the runtime errors so that normal flow of the application can be maintained


